# Normalize every text file to LF in the repository, regardless of what line endings a local
# editor/tool (Inkscape, MSYS2, etc.) saves on disk - matches what's already committed, avoids
# the git status/diff churn from core.autocrlf's own CRLF<->LF conversion looking inconsistent
# for files that end up with mixed or tool-specific endings. Binary files are auto-detected by
# git's own content sniffing and left untouched.
* text=auto eol=lf
